WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:13.304
Merry Christmas, everybody! Praise the Lord. Day 64. I have Diana here with me today, and we just wanted to come on today and tell you all Merry Christmas.

00:00:13.305 --> 00:00:31.185
We love you all so much. Thank you for your support. We appreciate all of you coming out every day to these videos to pray with us and intercede for the nations.

00:00:31.186 --> 00:00:38.900
Your support and love are so appreciated—praying for my daughter, for our family, and for me.

00:00:38.901 --> 00:00:47.442
The emails have been so kind lately, and I love the people sending earmuffs for Megan for the sound.

00:00:47.443 --> 00:00:55.289
A lot of times she won't wear those because she doesn't like things on her head, but we're getting there.

00:00:55.290 --> 00:00:58.754
We're just believing God she's going to be completely healed in 2024.

00:00:58.755 --> 00:01:10.919
We're closing this thing out, believing for the complete manifestation of Megan.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:13.152
She holds her ears like that throughout the day. For all of you who are so considerate, I know you're doing it out of love.

00:01:13.153 --> 00:01:19.239
It's just a habit, I think. Of course, the earmuffs are so nice, so we're going to try them.

00:01:19.240 --> 00:01:26.719
Sometimes you wonder if it was just the brand that she hasn't liked in the past, so she'll wear them for short periods.

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:35.419
Thank you all for helping my Megan out. What a blessing! So many people reaching out and trying to help.

00:01:35.420 --> 00:01:47.273
I just wanted to say thank you that you care. There are just a lot of kind, wonderful people on here with such great hearts.

00:01:47.274 --> 00:02:00.639
Thank you. I believe the best is yet to come. 2025 is coming and I'm anticipating great things.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:07.137
We want to show you this real quick. My wife went to the grocery store and got this cake.

00:02:07.138 --> 00:02:24.578
It's green, so I don't want it to disappear behind the green screen, but it says 'Happy Birthday Jesus.'We try every year to throw Jesus a birthday party with brownies or cookies, and this year Diana found a 'Happy Birthday Jesus'cake from the grocery store.

00:02:24.579 --> 00:02:45.966
It even has a manger on it. We'll sing happy birthday to Him as a family and do a full-blown birthday party for Him.

00:02:45.968 --> 00:02:53.859
He is our Lord and Savior. We wanted to come on and tell you all a very Merry Christmas.

00:02:53.860 --> 00:03:02.987
We're going to take communion with you, so if you want to get your communion ready, we're going to lift up the name of Jesus.

00:03:02.988 --> 00:03:12.639
Let's lift up the body. His body was broken and beaten for all our transgressions and iniquities.

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:19.051
The chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes, you're healed.

00:03:19.052 --> 00:03:35.219
In this Christmas season, it's even more of a gift to believe for your divine healing and to believe that everything broken in your body has been healed and made whole by His stripes.

00:03:35.220 --> 00:03:42.839
No matter what it is, nothing's too big and nothing's too small. Jesus paid the price for it all.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:52.646
According to Galatians, Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law, and the curse of the law is everything in Deuteronomy 28.

00:03:52.647 --> 00:04:03.163
I believe that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever, and that all things are possible to him who believes.

00:04:03.164 --> 00:04:14.039
This beautiful Christmas day, where all the gifts are being poured out on loved ones, Jesus gave the gift of His life.

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:29.949
He came as a child born in a manger and wrapped in swaddling clothes as a gift for humanity.

00:04:29.950 --> 00:04:39.758
He died for every single one of us so that we don't have to have all the bondage of this earth. He came to set the captives free.

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:56.436
The angels sang, 'Glory to God in the highest, peace on earth, goodwill to men.'Hallelujah, because of what He did on this very special day, Jesus paid the price.

00:04:56.437 --> 00:05:06.142
He lived 33 years and died on the cross after He was born. Oh, what a plan!

00:05:06.143 --> 00:05:20.439
What an amazing God we serve. He came to set the captives free and gave the ultimate sacrifice.

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:27.462
Thank you, Father, for giving Your Son. Thank you, Lord, for this body that was broken and beaten for us.

00:05:27.462 --> 00:05:39.610
Thank you for communion, that we are joint-heirs with You and we're able to be seated with You in the heavenlies, far above all principalities, powers, and might.

00:05:39.611 --> 00:05:50.242
We have dominion and authority over all satanic agendas. Father, I thank You that You said nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:05:50.243 --> 00:05:59.818
We take this body right now in the name of Jesus and we say, 'Happy Birthday, Jesus.'Thank You for this communion and for what You did for us.

00:05:59.819 --> 00:06:21.893
Thank You for coming to this earth as a baby. We don't have to be bound by sickness anymore.

00:06:21.894 --> 00:06:35.746
Now, Lord, we thank You for the blood. You said it was the cleansing flow that washed us as white as snow.

00:06:35.747 --> 00:06:42.240
It took care of all that sin and You made us spotless before You.

00:06:42.241 --> 00:06:47.411
Father, we thank You for that beautiful blood that flowed on Calvary's tree.

00:06:47.412 --> 00:06:57.726
It flowed down and cleansed Diana and me, and it cleansed every single one of you. We're so grateful for Your life and Your blood.

00:06:57.727 --> 00:07:08.471
We thank You, Lord, that as we confess our sins, You are faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:07:08.472 --> 00:07:14.962
He's written our names in the Lamb's Book of Life. It's Your blood that sets us free.

00:07:14.963 --> 00:07:31.576
By the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony, we take this blood in the name of Jesus.

00:07:31.577 --> 00:07:50.582
We give You praise, Father, for Your presence and the anointing of the Holy Spirit.

00:07:50.583 --> 00:08:18.362
We love You and we magnify You. Happy birthday to You, dear Jesus!

00:08:18.363 --> 00:08:51.944
One day we'll celebrate His birthday with Him in person; I look forward to that.

00:08:51.945 --> 00:09:12.165
We honor the Lord today. Thank You for all You've done for us this year.

00:09:12.166 --> 00:09:32.302
Thank You for President Trump and the new administration coming in, giving us another opportunity and a season of grace.

00:09:32.303 --> 00:09:41.404
Sister Billye talked about the gifts being distributed on the 25th, and we believe something supernatural has happened today.

00:09:41.405 --> 00:09:48.993
We pray you felt His presence in your house today as you're spending time with your loved ones.

00:09:48.994 --> 00:10:00.036
Maybe you're alone, but you are not alone because we are with you. If you don't have any family, we are your family.

00:10:00.037 --> 00:10:11.353
Diana, Braden, and I are loving on you through the camera, telling you that you've got what it takes. Jesus has a plan for your life.

00:10:11.354 --> 00:10:25.770
You may feel alone in the natural, but there's somebody in a little house in Oklahoma believing God with you.

00:10:25.771 --> 00:10:38.667
2025 is going to be an amazing year for you. Like we always say, Diana, put a smile on your face and a song on your heart.

00:10:38.668 --> 00:10:47.248
There are good days ahead for the body of Christ. We had a lady send us a letter.

00:10:47.249 --> 00:10:55.630
She is alone, her husband has passed, and her little canary passed away recently.

00:10:55.631 --> 00:11:12.739
She's having a hard time, and her letter was so touching. There are so many people going through so much right now.

00:11:12.740 --> 00:11:24.163
Even the loss of a little bird matters; she wanted to know if it would be in heaven because she misses her friend.

00:11:24.164 --> 00:11:46.054
I promised I wasn't going to cry, but it really touched me. William Branham talked about this before he went home to be with the Lord. Sister Billye told us this story.

00:11:46.055 --> 00:12:05.898
If an animal was precious to you on this earth, God has so much compassion and love for us that those animals are waiting for you in heaven.

00:12:05.899 --> 00:12:15.824
The Lord showed William Branham that those animals, even during the Rapture, are so important to you that they are going to be taken too.

00:12:15.825 --> 00:12:32.580
He gives you the desires of your heart, and if it's your desire to have your pet with you, the Lord's going to see to it.

00:12:32.581 --> 00:12:57.494
He cares about the smallest details in your life. He has it all figured out.

00:12:57.495 --> 00:13:18.559
I believe the little parakeets, sparrows, and even a little 'Peanut the pocket squirrel'like Bob Ross used to carry—God cares about them.

00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:45.927
I'll never forget when my dog died when I was Braden's age. It meant so much to me and hurt so bad at the time, but I gave it over to the Lord.

00:13:45.928 --> 00:14:09.243
When I heard the testimony from Billye while we were sitting around the table talking about the Rapture, we were all rejoicing over the fact that soon and very soon, we're about to go see the King.

00:14:09.244 --> 00:14:18.115
Our loved ones and our loved animals are going to come right alongside us.

00:14:18.116 --> 00:14:33.114
William Branham saw many amazing things before he went to be with the Lord.

00:14:33.115 --> 00:14:49.180
He even saw egg-shaped cars in the 1940s and 50s that were driving themselves, like Teslas.

00:14:49.181 --> 00:14:57.968
He said when Jesus comes back, what the Lord showed him in that vision is that a woman would be running the White House.

00:14:57.969 --> 00:15:04.235
Everybody thought it was Kamala Harris he was seeing, but it wasn't time yet.

00:15:04.236 --> 00:15:26.193
Who's coming in 2028? I don't know, but it would be neat if that vision lines up.

00:15:26.194 --> 00:15:39.247
God has a plan for everything. He wants you to be filled with joy, not dread or anxiety.

00:15:39.248 --> 00:15:51.226
We are looking up, for our redemption is drawing nigh, folks.

00:15:51.227 --> 00:15:59.719
In 2025, we're not just going to survive; we're going to thrive.

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:18.534
In 2024, the Lord told me I would soar and there would be a great open door, and it has been exactly that.

00:16:18.535 --> 00:16:39.599
We have gone from glory to glory this year. I'm believing 2025 will be a supernatural year of God's provision.

00:16:39.600 --> 00:16:53.560
Heaven on Earth! I'm believing for healings, demonstrations, and manifestations.

00:16:53.561 --> 00:17:11.120
There's going to be a great harvest of souls. I want to give you all hope to get excited about the days ahead.

00:17:11.121 --> 00:17:20.223
We pray this video blessed you. We thank You, Lord, for healing, wholeness, and wellness over every household.

00:17:20.224 --> 00:17:59.639
We pray they'll hear Your voice concerning investments. The Holy Spirit will lead and guide you into all things.

00:17:59.640 --> 00:18:05.262
You're going to know them by their fruit, and you're not going to be led astray in these last days.

00:18:05.263 --> 00:18:22.358
I pray for discernment over your minds today, that the inward voice of the Holy Spirit would be so loud.

00:18:22.359 --> 00:19:24.048
You'll know exactly what to do. You're free from addictions, from cigarettes and alcohol to gambling, pornography, and lust.

00:19:24.049 --> 00:19:37.199
You are bound no more by those demonic strongholds. You're not bound by depression or anxiety.

00:19:37.200 --> 00:20:47.079
We believe for promotions, raises, bonuses, and growth in businesses.

00:20:47.080 --> 00:20:57.036
We believe every seed you sowed in 2024, you're going to reap in 2025 exceedingly and abundantly.

00:20:57.037 --> 00:21:08.793
Thank You, Father, for children and for marriages being restored.

00:21:08.794 --> 00:21:11.834
We pray over President Trump as he has a beautiful Christmas.

00:21:11.835 --> 00:21:22.079
We thank You that no more wars are caused while the current administration is in the White House.

00:21:22.080 --> 00:21:36.517
We call peace over Russia and the Ukraine deal and over our southern borders.

00:21:36.518 --> 00:21:56.635
2025 will be an amazing year. If you're new here, please subscribe and click that notification bell.

00:21:56.636 --> 00:22:09.513
We're creating a Vietnam channel, a Chinese channel, a South Korean channel, a Russian channel, and a Philippines channel.

00:22:09.514 --> 00:22:26.840
We're doing it by the grace of God and through your support. The links are in the description.

00:22:26.841 --> 00:23:12.651
Asia is going to catch on fire for Jesus! Tomorrow is Diana's birthday, the 26th.

00:23:12.652 --> 00:23:25.552
It always made her feel special being so close to Jesus's birthday.

00:23:25.553 --> 00:23:41.430
She's still young at heart. We've made it through a lot, and we keep going.

00:23:41.431 --> 00:23:55.130
God is good. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much, and we love you. Merry Christmas!

